{"ha0cbf090g37c5g40fag8d22g7812acb196e4": ["We lost Andrick. Sir.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "cb7e1953-93da-4cdc-3161-c1d8972b040d"], "hb3631f1agc13eg4cd2gb9e3gc02efe759e75": ["We lost Andrick. Ma'am.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "cb7e1953-93da-4cdc-3161-c1d8972b040d"], "hf02319b7gef35g4478g8adegbf3d488a1e84": ["He's... with Edowin now, right? He's with the Absolute.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "fb352c81-b826-7e47-0611-9e2b2f4b42ae"], "hd2e511f2g3789g4da4gba01g5cb5ef0c57a4": ["That's right. He's safe now. Blessed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "0c85a3a4-34d3-1d76-7317-234679b589a2"], "ha1072329ge79bg4706gb6d0gce61f1e915eb": ["Thank you.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "f5a609e5-2ed4-7cbe-8006-1c39afef195a"], "hdc247db0g6358g4272gb039g7b2cd1fda383": ["What would you have of me now, sir?", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "eb67d928-a154-a641-0d8f-141da6fd9203"], "hb4fc8a72g5816g44a9ga732gc7a010c9a8df": ["What would you have of me now, madam?", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "eb67d928-a154-a641-0d8f-141da6fd9203"], "hb963c2e6gc994g43a4ga19dgca5439e4e039": ["Find the nearest stronghold and report on your mission.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "72552384-4662-56b1-519d-f7121c01fa78"], "hf2344b50gcac6g432ega7d5g3e9702e68984": ["Edowin told us there was a camp of faithful goblins nearby. It'll do me good to be among allies.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "9c2bc6e0-fb2f-38e1-264e-3143f29bfa99"], "hb1618588g3c4fg43a5g99c5gc5afbf4ae2ea": ["Go safely, True Soul.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "020f0a03-1ff1-827c-bb33-11e35028abe8"], "haacd537fg0165g4ba7ga40ag9c9f2235cd91": ["Continue your duties in the area - whatever those are.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "01ec8530-128f-7245-6cf0-25cc22669238"], "hd2b5957agd2ddg44b0g99c7g7a8a2af3c403": ["Yes. That's what Edowin would say. And what Andrick would've done, too.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "f778b6c3-b0ea-de53-bd7b-4d830666d33b"], "hfc5a9e4dg5252g4d22ga1cdg95d95dc6da22": ["Go safely, True Soul.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "3baab6aa-0f39-fed0-2613-83aa87f01508"], "h39f0754ag6ba6g407ega8ddg40d1c94b74a9": ["He died honourably. You should be proud.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "a0caf8d0-cded-efcf-b3ea-966939a67423"], "h9874100ag6ea1g46e4gb9ebgfb62ddbce7db": ["Perhaps. Who truly knows the ways of our god?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "8071b2d1-d178-dee0-c6cd-d7a9a81890c0"], "h8cad4e42g5253g49e0g9fe9g36bb25b645ab": ["I suppose... I suppose the Absolute keeps some mysteries from us all.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "bbc4ed88-3c70-e98d-96cb-d4a33905e468"], "ha02dd036ga6f2g4962g8f36g187a1325897c": ["It's... dead. We couldn't have done it without you. Thank you.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "aa141c56-1acd-ffce-437f-9ce0497bce60"], "ha690c1d1gd322g4530ga211g55d44b4ef5db": ["Yes, we'll praise you in our prayers, True Soul.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "134f8f24-eecb-42db-3a0e-d25af54f0be3"], "h7df3172fg145ag4a1dg899fg1f4ffc7a993d": ["I wish Edowin were here. He would have been honoured to fight alongside you.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "ac8e6078-b2f5-bb78-6978-6df900bfdc82"], "hdf00156ag67a0g4e35g87deg07307b9430a7": ["What would you have of us now, sir?", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "0076ab6f-8c2c-08cb-2c94-1ea202bc5e06"], "h457eadeegde1dg4bb0gad61ge4174ee74b17": ["What would you have of us now, madam?", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "0076ab6f-8c2c-08cb-2c94-1ea202bc5e06"], "h8ef0efaag3a16g4152g8de9g0b11bff8def2": ["Find the nearest stronghold and report on your mission.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "6c5ef09c-b3a7-9d17-2865-ccaf78d75275"], "h04f9ed28g0f8dg4e5bg8517g273fe4568635": ["Edowin told us there was a camp of faithful goblins nearby. We'll find safe harbour there. He'd... want us among friends.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "ab9cdd52-5fa3-2d45-47f3-32a1a51575b0"], "h06031555g080eg4f39gbbe8g93c08eedc146": ["Absolute protect you.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "3485093f-6aa9-7267-61e3-5ff7e68d052b"], "hdcc9d17cg5b3dg4213ga4a9g6ed561e934df": ["What were you doing before the owlbear attacked?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "14cce963-1776-c21c-b658-3aa8f3359dd6"], "h07997ddag6085g48d1ga974g9e5622fa124a": ["We were sent to look for fugitives. Some survivors from a crashed ship a ways west along the Chionthar.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "7c8fc36c-f380-58bd-124a-8799cde0be4c"], "h05b41bc9ga869g4e00gbdb5g4391aaebf0f3": ["The Absolute wants them found, one way or another.", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "78b8f1ea-9f38-41b0-94fd-5947131d1323"], "h0097b2e3g1f93g4a2fga4d3gec546a58a494": ["It seems you've found one of your fugitives. Me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "bbd71906-a82b-7e1d-9c20-c526770ee53f"], "hf9d009a7g79d2g4c9ag9315g5347b42ddfc3": ["What? <i>You...?</i> But that means... I have to stop you. For the Absolute!", "2c9b967d-fbaa-43c0-9461-3e1598b5fbe1", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "239e8269-e5a5-7c64-5846-6de0b068f546"], "hf77a1902g631cg4afegb6c8g734875a7067e": ["Carry on with your hunt, then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "820575bf-eef4-a0e3-12b7-f556cfb8edad"], "h3c8bb838g7921g4f6cg9c08g2eba5810cae3": ["Absolute protect you.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "f29f0f21-5c8e-23d0-85e4-8184bb0716c3"], "h81bfff22gdd13g4fecg964cg62f2d5cbfe6d": ["Resume your duties in the area - whatever those are.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "bc6f196f-acbd-0200-72e9-86728ebd9e80"], "h56769d4bg4295g4ac7g8384ga6b716c922ca": ["Absolute protect us...", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "43d1a39b-4838-2c42-c7ba-2675c577f533"], "hcb91bf80g3d9cg4ee7g9cb7gc7b1ff19c2ca": ["The beast's ahead. We need to get closer.", "d4a3b125-2b03-4fe8-bab2-7e485390bd49", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_PriestOfTheConqueringGod_Cultist002_InCave.html", "d6545967-f2a1-1a68-7f04-220e99c43420"]}